<template>

  <n-grid cols="1 400:2 600:3" item-responsive>

    <n-grid-item>
      <n-button>
        <template #icon>
          <n-icon>
            <add-icon />
          </n-icon>
        </template>
        添加楼栋
      </n-button>
      <n-button>
        <template #icon>
          <n-icon>
            <edit-icon />
          </n-icon>
        </template>
        修改楼栋
      </n-button>
      <n-button>
        <template #icon>
          <n-icon>
            <delete-icon />
          </n-icon>
        </template>
        删除楼栋
      </n-button>  
    </n-grid-item>

  </n-grid>

</template>

<script setup>
// 引入 vue
import { ref } from 'vue'
// 引入 naive-ui 组件
import {
  NButton, NIcon, NGrid, NGridItem
} from 'naive-ui'
// 引入图标 
import {
  Add16Regular as AddIcon,
  Edit16Regular as EditIcon,
  Delete16Regular as DeleteIcon
} from '@vicons/fluent'
</script>

<script>
export default {
  name: 'HousingManagementLayout'
}
</script>

<style>

</style>
